---
title: Persian-Inspired Chickpea and Chicken Tenders Stew with Toasted Garlic Flatbreads
description: Middle Eastern spice-roasted carrots are the star of this warming tomato-based stew. Hearty chicken, toasted almonds and a spicy chili-garlic sauce are the perfect toppers for this crave-worthy dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-filets-de-poulet-et-de-pois-chiches-a-la-perse-89539ab9.jpg
